{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-27-Virtual-Memory-3/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"paging-sharing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#paging-sharing\" aria-label=\"paging sharing permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌paging sharing</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>여러 프로세스가 특정 page 공유 가능</li>\n<li>non-continous allocation이라서 가능</li>\n<li>Protection bit 사용(어떤 프로세스가 어떤 일을 하거나 어느정도 권한이 있는지 적어두는 공간)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"공유-가능-page\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B3%B5%EC%9C%A0-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5-page\" aria-label=\"공유 가능 page permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>공유 가능 page</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>procedure pages\n<ul>\n<li>pure code</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>data page - read only data - read write data\r\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/wjdtmfgh/post/0b4a4256-a08b-445d-8e55-3f8205b5af1c/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"segmentation-system\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#segmentation-system\" aria-label=\"segmentation system permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌segmentation system</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>프로그램들을 논리적 block으로 분할, block크기가 서로 다를 수 있음</li>\n<li>메모리를 미리 분할 하지 않음(VPM), 메모리 동적 분할</li>\n<li>sharing, protection이 용이</li>\n<li>no internal fragmentation</li>\n<li>external fragmentation 발생 가능\r\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/wjdtmfgh/post/6ffe9d6f-c8b3-4b02-80b1-a6ee73796821/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"address-mapping\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#address-mapping\" aria-label=\"address mapping permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>address mapping</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>virtual address : v = (s, d)</li>\n<li>segement Map Table(SMT)</li>\n<li>paging system과 동일 단, segment length(크기) / protection bits 존재\r\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/wjdtmfgh/post/b957b4f3-086a-4f83-b056-8a2e6d7ff7b5/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>프로세스의 SMT가 저장되어 있는 주소 b 접근</li>\n<li>SMT에서 segment s의 entry 찾기\n<ul>\n<li>s의 entry = b + s * entrySize</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>찾아진 entry에 대해 다음 단계들을 순차적으로 진행\r\n3-1. 존재 비트 0인경우 : segment fault\r\nswap device로부터 해당 segment 메모리로 적재\r\n3-2. d가 segment길이 초과할 경우 처리 모듈 시행\r\n3-3. protection bit 검사하여 허가 되지 않은 연산인 경우 처리 모듈 시행\r\n3-4. SMT에서 segment 시작 위치 a 참조</li>\n<li>실제 주소 r 계산, r = a + d</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"paging-vs-segmentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#paging-vs-segmentation\" aria-label=\"paging vs segmentation permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌paging vs segmentation</h2>\n<h2 id=\"paging\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#paging\" aria-label=\"paging permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>paging</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>simple</li>\n<li>low overhead</li>\n<li>no logical concept partition</li>\n<li>complex page sharing</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"segmentation-system-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#segmentation-system-1\" aria-label=\"segmentation system 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>segmentation system</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>high management overhead</li>\n<li>logical concept partition</li>\n<li>simple sharing</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#paging-sharing\">📌paging sharing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B3%B5%EC%9C%A0-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5-page\">공유 가능 page</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#segmentation-system\">📌segmentation system</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#address-mapping\">address mapping</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#paging-vs-segmentation\">📌paging vs segmentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#paging\">paging</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#segmentation-system-1\">segmentation system</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Virtual Memory 3","date":"2023년 02월 26일","tags":["CS"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-27-Virtual-Memory-3/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-24-Virtual-Memory-1/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"Virtual Memory 1","date":"2023-02-24 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-27-Virtual-Memory-4/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"Virtual Memory 1","date":"2023-02-27 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}